Pysexy are the python language bindings for libsexy,
the experimental-new-cool-gtk-widgets-which-are-crude-hacks library.

No doc available yet, but the function name should be pretty self-explanative.

REQUIREMENTS
------------
libsexy-0.1.2 or above, and dependencies of it, such as gtk and glib
python-2.3 or above
pygtk-2.6 or above

LIBSEXY
-------
libsexy is mainly maintained by Christian Hammond <chipx86@chipx86.com>
You can retreive it using SVN:

svn co "http://osiris.chipx86.com/svn/osiris-misc/trunk/libsexy/"
